title: Ep. - 271 - HANNAH BERNER REVIEWS THE BACHELOR REVIEW OF REAL HOUSEWIVES OF BEVERLY HILLS
description:
Kate reviews David Foster: Off the Record on Netflix.

 

Megan Shanley reviews the latest episode of Real Housewives of Beverly Hills.

 

Hannah Berner from Summer House on Bravo reviews The Bachelor season 20 with Ben Higgins, talks about why reality stars pursue love relationships on TV, and about her day with Luann DeLesseps on Shelter Island.
